Subject: [PATCH] wifi: ath12k: Dump additional PDEV receive rate HTT stats
Git-commit: 7a3e8eec8d183d7b293bfb69caab9f213e0a6bbd
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Support to dump additional PDEV receive rate stats through HTT debugfs
stats type 30.

Sample output:

